    public abstract class ARecipeTypeMapper<R extends net.minecraft.item.crafting.IRecipe<?>>
extends ABaseRecipeMapper<R>
implements moze_intel.projecte.api.mapper.recipe.IRecipeTypeMapper
    An abstract class used for converting IRecipes to EMC conversion maps.

    This function has a few helper variables: ABaseRecipeMapper.recipeID, ABaseRecipeMapper.mapper and ABaseRecipeMapper.fakeGroupManager

    This class follows closely to BaseRecipeTypeMapper with added function for special recipes with ItemStack and/or FluidStack outputs.

    To overwrite output, override method getOutput(IRecipe) to overwrite input, override method getIngredients(IRecipe)

    For an example on how to handle recipes with multiple outputs, look at ImmersiveEngineeringAddon
